feedback_content: Sandy, I want to discuss some areas in your recent project where there’s room for improvement. I've noticed some missed deadlines and a few inaccuracies in the monthly reports which have led to setbacks in our team’s schedule. It's important to ensure that all information is double-checked and submitted on time. I know you have the capability to handle these tasks well, as you've shown in previous projects.

Sandy, we need to address the recent issues with your work performance directly. The missed deadlines and errors in the monthly reports are unacceptable and have compromised our team's ability to meet its objectives. We've discussed the importance of accuracy and punctuality before, yet these problems persist. It is critical that you immediately improve your performance in these areas. Let's be clear: further failure to meet expectations will result in more severe consequences.
